started to tell their story,

13:57.488 --> 14:00.622
their life, they
started to talk.

14:03.712 --> 14:06.497
She had always been
an Indian classical dancer,

14:06.541 --> 14:09.022
and she saw
that the discipline

14:09.065 --> 14:12.199
and the whole use
of their bodies

14:12.242 --> 14:15.463
was quite empowering
for these young women,

14:15.506 --> 14:18.988
and it became
therapeutic in nature.

14:45.101 --> 14:46.407
And then I found that,

14:46.450 --> 14:49.279
"Oh, there is dance
movement therapy."

14:49.323 --> 14:51.238
It has a 40-years history,

14:51.281 --> 14:55.242
and I was kind of, "Wow.
I am on the right track."

