17:11.247 --> 17:14.294
and I wanted them to be able
to go to university.

17:14.337 --> 17:19.125
I went back to college and made
wire crosses from my dorm
room and sold them,

17:19.168 --> 17:24.086
and in a few months I made
enough money to send those
two girls to school.

17:24.130 --> 17:29.787
