hell holes to be in.

24:43.307 --> 24:46.528
And then they are being forced
to attend to these customers

24:46.572 --> 24:49.792
who come sometimes
10, 15, 20 in a day.

25:13.294 --> 25:18.473
I got kidnapped from Delhi
when I was four years old.

25:18.517 --> 25:22.564
I was taken from here
to there and people used
me like currency.

25:26.002 --> 25:29.353
I was just like a ten rupee
note passed from hand to hand,

25:29.397 --> 25:31.878
going from one place to another.

25:31.921 --> 25:34.533
That's how I was passed
from one house to another.

25:36.622 --> 25:40.364
At times when I woke up, I
found myself in dark rooms.

25:42.584 --> 25:48.024
I lived with my traffickers
from the age of 5 until
I was 13 years old.

25:48.068 --> 25:51.375
Then the police caught me and
brought me to the shelter home.

25:56.163 --> 25:59.601
Most of the children
who are trafficked

25:59.645 --> 26:03.126
into the brothels
and red light area,

26:03.170 --> 26:07.870
first, they cut off from their
body, the disconnection.

26:07.914 --> 26:09.611
They start to hate their body.

26:26.106 --> 26:28.456
Work with the body
is so important

26:28.499 --> 26:32.634
because when the exploitation,
the violence, and the abuse--

26:32.678 --> 26:36.551
anything that's happened,
it's a tremendous
physical trauma.

26:37.726 --> 26:41.295
We really do not
have that much tool

26:41.338 --> 26:44.603
available to work on
the physical trauma.

